title: Episode 143: The Big O (Feat. Oloni)

description:
An award winning sex relationship blogger, Oloni, sits with the ladies of Lip Service for this weeks episode. They discuss sugar daddy's, trying new things in bed, reasons for breaking up that isn't cheating, and much more! Oloni believes monogamous relationships are overrated...do you agree?
